quran[34]{c,v,t,f}:
  56,17,"Wakitumikiwa na wavulana wa ujana wa milele, <sup foot_note=17>17</sup>","[17] Wakiwazungukia kwa kuwakhudumia vijana watakao baki milele hivyo hivyo,"
  56,18,"Kwa vikombe na mabirika na bilauri za vinywaji kutoka chemchem safi. <sup foot_note=18>18</sup>","[18] Nao wamechukua vikombe na mabirika yaliyo jaa vinywaji vya Peponi, na bilauri zenye mvinyo kutoka chemchem zinazo miminika,"
  56,19,"Hawataumwa kichwa kwa vinywaji hivyo wala hawatoleweshwa. <sup foot_note=19>19</sup>","[19] Vinywaji hivyo haviwaletei kuumwa kichwa wala kutokwa akili kwa ulevi."
  56,20,"Na matunda wayapendayo, <sup foot_note=20>20</sup>","[20] Na matunda ya kila namna wanayo yapenda na wanayo yaona;"
  56,21,"Na nyama za ndege kama wanavyo tamani. <sup foot_note=21>21</sup>","[21] Na nyama za ndege kama zinavyo tamani nafsi zao."
  56,22,"Na Mahurulaini, <sup foot_note=22>22</sup>","[22] Na wanawake wenye macho ya vikombe,"
  56,23,"Walio kama mfano wa lulu zilio hifadhiwa. <sup foot_note=23>23</sup>","[23] Kama mfano wa lulu zilio hifadhiwa katika chaza, kwa usafi wao na urembo wao."
  56,24,"Ni malipo kwa waliyo kuwa wakiyatenda. <sup foot_note=24>24</sup>","[24] Watapewa haya kuwa ni malipo kwa mambo mema waliyo kuwa wakiyatenda duniani."
  56,25,"Humo hawatasikia porojo wala maneno ya dhambi, <sup foot_note=25>25</sup>","[25] Huko Peponi hawatasikia maneno yasiyo kuwa na maana, wala masimulizi ya kumtia dhambini mwenye kuyasikia."
  56,26,"Isipo kuwa maneno ya Salama, Salama. <sup foot_note=26>26</sup>","[26] Ila watalo sikia ni kauli ya wao kwa wao: Tunakusalimuni kwa Salama."
  56,27,"Na wale wa mkono wa kulia, ni yepi yatakuwa ya wa kuliani? <sup foot_note=27>27</sup>","[27] Na watu wa mkono wa kulia, hapana ajuaye nini malipo ya watu wa kuliani."
  56,28,"Katika mikunazi isiyo na miba, <sup foot_note=28>28</sup>","[28] Katika miti ya mikunazi iliyo katwa miba yake,"
  56,29,"Na migomba iliyo pangiliwa, <sup foot_note=29>29</sup>","[29] Na migomba iliyo pangika na ndizi zake zimepandana juu ya mikungu,"
  56,30,"Na kivuli kilicho tanda, <sup foot_note=30>30</sup>","[30] Na kivuli kilicho enea wala hakiondoki,"
  56,31,"Na maji yanayo miminika, <sup foot_note=31>31</sup>","[31] Na maji yanayo miminika karibu yao popote wayatakapo,"
  56,32,"Na matunda mengi, <sup foot_note=32>32</sup>","[32] Na matunda ya namna nyingi na kabila nyingi yasiyo tindikia wakati wowote,"
  56,33,"Hayatindikii wala hayakatazwi, <sup foot_note=33>33</sup>","[33] Wala hazuiwiliwi ayatakayo,"
  56,34,"Na matandiko yaliyo nyanyuliwa. <sup foot_note=34>34</sup>","[34] Na matandiko yaliyo nyanyuliwa ya starehe."
  56,35,"Hakika Sisi tutawaumba (Mahurulaini) upya, <sup foot_note=35>35</sup>","[35] Hakika Sisi tulianza kuwaumba Mahurulaini mwanzo,"
  56,36,"Na tutawafanya vijana, <sup foot_note=36>36</sup>","[36] Na tukawafanya kuwa ni vijana,"
  56,37,"Wanapendana na waume zao, hirimu moja. <sup foot_note=37>37</sup>","[37] Wenye kupendwa na waume zao, wenye umri ulio karibiana,"
  56,38,"Kwa ajili ya watu wa kuliani. <sup foot_note=38>38</sup>","[38] Wa tayari kwa neema ya watu wa kuliani."
  56,39,"Fungu kubwa katika wa mwanzo, <sup foot_note=39>39</sup>","[39] Watu wa kulia ni wengi katika mataifu yaliyo kwisha tangulia,"
  56,40,"Na fungu kubwa katika wa mwisho. <sup foot_note=40>40</sup>","[40] Na kikundi kikubwa katika umma wa Muhammad."
  56,41,"Na watu wa kushotoni; je ni yepi ya wa kushotoni? <sup foot_note=41>41</sup>","[41] Na watu wa kushoto, hapana anaye jua nini adhabu ya watu wa kushoto."
  56,42,"Katika upepo wa moto, na maji yanayo chemka, <sup foot_note=42>42</sup>","[42] Watakuwa kwenye upepo umoto utakao wazunguka, unao penya katika tundu za mwili, na maji yaliyo chemshwa motoni wayanywe na wamiminiwe vichwani,"
  56,43,"Na kivuli cha moshi mweusi, <sup foot_note=43>43</sup>","[43] Na katika kivuli cha kiza cheusi cha moshi umoto,"
  56,44,"Si cha kuburudisha wala kustarehesha. <sup foot_note=44>44</sup>","[44] Hapana ubaridi wa kupunguza joto la hewa, wala huruma ya kuwaletea nafuu wanapo vuta pumzi."
  56,45,"Hakika hao walikuwa kabla ya haya wakiishi maisha ya anasa. <sup foot_note=45>45</sup>","[45] Hakika hao kabla ya haya walikuwa wamepita kiasi katika kustarehea neema za duniani, wamepumbaa hawataki kumt'ii Mwenyezi Mungu Mtukufu."
  56,46,"Na walikuwa wakishikilia kufanya madhambi makubwa, <sup foot_note=46>46</sup>","[46] Na walikuwa wameshikilia daima kufanya dhambi kubwa kabisa, kwani waliapa kwa Mwenyezi Mungu kwamba kabisa Mwenyezi Mungu hatamfufua aliye kufa."
  56,47,"Na walikuwa wakisema: Tutakapo kufa na tukawa udongo na mafupa, ati ndio tutafufuliwa? <sup foot_note=47>47</sup>","[47] Na walikuwa wakisema kwa kukanusha kurejea tena: Ati tutafufuliwa baada ya kwisha kufa, na baadhi ya miili yetu ikisha kuwa udongo na mengine mifupa iliyo chakaa? Ati sisi tutarudishwa tuwe hai mara ya pili?"
  56,48,"Au baba zetu wa zamani? <sup foot_note=48>48</sup>","[48] Ati tutafufuliwa sisi na baba zetu wa zamani walio kwisha kuwa udongo ulio tapanyika na umepotea katika ardhi?"
  56,49,"Sema: Hakika wa zamani na wa mwisho <sup foot_note=49>49</sup>","[49] Waambie kwa kuwajibu kukanusha kwao: Hakika wa zamani na wa mwisho, ambao nyinyi ni katika jumla ya hao,"
  56,50,"Bila ya shaka watakusanywa kwa wakati wa siku maalumu. <sup foot_note=50>50</sup>","[50] Nyote mtakusanywa katika wakati wa siku malumu, na wala hamtoipita."

